description:
This query works ok on tiny datasets, but never finishes on larger ones (for example: SUMO)
I see the problem only if default graph is specified as parameter to SPARQL-endpoint.
CONSTRUCT {
    ?s ?p ?o
}
where {
    ?s ?p ?o .
    {
        select distinct ?s where {?s [] []} limit 10
    }
}

Both internal query and outer query with result of internal query supplied explicitly (via FILTER(IN())) work instantaneously.
